{"tid":2067820,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《Produce 101》第二季無詐欺嫌疑！韓檢方不起訴安俊英！","createTime":"2020-06-17T09:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T09:50:21.000Z","uid":68678,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f621e462bc8b7b5bd8fd68f22d804e7d95a2d379","tid":2067820,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"根據韓媒報導，負責《Produce101》第二季造假案的首爾中央地方檢察院，宣布不會起訴節目PD安俊英與CP金勇範。<br />\n<br />\n金勇範等人涉嫌操縱投票造假選拔第3-4季最終成員全員、第2季1人，並于去年12月被移交審判。檢察機關調查組認為，與第3-4季不同，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩人在第二季中僅對一名訓練生的投票數進行了僞造</strong></span></span>，檢方認為其行為不構成以不當獲利為目標的欺詐，因此決定不予起訴。<br />\n<br />\n二人之前因《PD》第三季與第四季投票造假一審，分別被判處了兩年有期徒刑和一年八個月有期徒刑，但安俊英與檢方均在不久前提出上訴，此案二審將在不久後開庭。但網友對於僅一人做票就不構成欺詐這個理由，似乎並不接受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>導好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又fake晒班傻鳩衝出嚟柒</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2483cd310fb93822c87caf7d39fa3327195a06ae","tid":2067820,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"四捨五入當冇得唔得"},{"pid":"d737da232957c554ff747802fef5a47f625f8b9e","tid":2067820,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2483cd310fb93822c87caf7d39fa3327195a06ae","tid":2067820,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"四捨五入當冇得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣 PD冇造馬 梁sir冇叫雞 ✊🏻💘"},{"pid":"d595e8fdefb18c5c07781396bcced7aa009e5597","tid":2067820,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"估唔到你搵左咁耐"},{"pid":"86cba87f9956383e2dcacc04f26b5cac3be3c309","tid":2067820,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:18:02.000Z","msg":"唔係好熟 有冇總結<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" c